Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.21,0:14:50.52,sogtra,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}啦啦哩啦 啦哩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:53.87,sogtra,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}发现 小小的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:15:01.04,sogtra,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}想在天空飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:04.93,sogtra,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}明明 总是想要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:08.41,sogtra,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}去往某个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:15.21,sogtra,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}却总是躲在你的身后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:22.31,sogtra,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}在安静的森林里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:29.69,sogtra,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}一个人 迎着风歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:33.82,sogtra,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}如果能稍微离远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:37.33,sogtra,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}这样 凝视着我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:44.88,sogtra,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)}就悄悄告诉你重要的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.21,0:14:50.52,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}ララリラ ラリラ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:53.87,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}空 羽ばたいて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:15:01.04,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}小さな私を見つけた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:04.93,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}どこかに いつも
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:08.41,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}行きたいのに
