Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.75,0:00:11.88,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背上的羽翼　已经与你一同消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:19.68,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞翔时的记忆　却无法像擦伤一样消去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:35.99,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你寻回　是我一直所想之事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.99,0:00:43.66,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你不随时间的浊流　被浪冲走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.66,0:00:51.46,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法说出些许回忆　始终无依无靠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:59.47,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残留下的些许眼泪　却一定无法传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.47,0:01:05.73,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的泪滴　也将坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.73,0:01:13.61,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然间黑夜被撕裂　光芒飞散于空中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:21.58,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洁净如洗的太阳　温柔地照耀着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:26.21,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀抱着你一起前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.93,0:22:39.27,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After the rain　等到雨停了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.44,0:22:46.53,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,across the rainbow　就飞越彩虹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.53,0:22:53.58,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在彩虹被蓝天遮掩前　告诉它
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.37,0:23:02.00,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.21,0:23:10.59,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为何会被忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:16.06,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝物的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.48,0:23:25.98,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After the rain　等到雨停了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:33.24,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,across the rainbow　从哪里开始说起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.24,0:23:40.16,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲伤不会消失　所以悄悄地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.12,0:23:49.47,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这些点缀在快乐的回忆里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.70,0:04:00.60,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,250)}{\fad(1000,0)}门的里面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.29,0:01:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家 是由统治大山另一边领地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.98,0:01:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有斗蛇军队的大公军来保卫的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.16,0:01:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.27,0:01:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那边也查一查
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 听说您找我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁甘 你看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.29,0:02:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是放在我们大公领
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给真王陛下的贡品中的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.13,0:02:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父拟草
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父拟草?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.99,0:02:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会有这种毒草
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天收到封恐吓信 说是有毒物混入了贡品里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查后便找到了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.41,0:02:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐吓信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然向拥有斗蛇军队的我们发恐吓信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是何人如此大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血秽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无凭无据不要乱说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是血秽那群人一直意图向真王陛下造反
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.89,0:03:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时不时会惹出一些事端来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他们也曾打过斗蛇蛋的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.81,0:03:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血秽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁甘 关于这件事 由我来调查
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 为了保护真王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就去操练兵法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.73,0:03:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能毒已经在这个国家里蔓延开了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在远离大公领
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王国的最西端的山脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住着位养蜂人约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在约翰这里展开新生活的艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在准备搬家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二 三
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清洁工作先放一放
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来帮我一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 里面的那房间我还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个房间不用打扫了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.00,0:04:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 其实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前都瞒着你是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闹鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有恐怖的妖怪出现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.51,0:05:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要看妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔让我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.05,0:05:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好不容易才把它们关起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能进去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快过来帮忙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 为什么要搬家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道我的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饲养蜜蜂 然后贩卖蜂蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.76,0:05:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜蜂是怎么酿蜜的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 从花朵里收集花蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再酿成蜂蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些花何时会开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:05:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.07,0:05:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 这里马上就要到夏天了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 夏知草都开了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 快到夏天时这一带就会盛开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.83,0:06:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 好像在哪里也看过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个花只会在这附近开的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们养蜂人 以这些花为信号 往山上迁移
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这样才搬家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 跟着花走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种花的花蜜甜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要总是突然做些危险的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能舔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是舔上一口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让肚子痛上三天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那滋味可不好受哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔是不是舔过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.84,0:07:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是舔过 当然不会知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说 要是这样舔了的话会中毒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 微小量的话还可以入药用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既是毒药也是良药
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样一种花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔你知道的好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着 我们去准备迁移多奇和诺诺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.74,0:07:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能要多花点功夫了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子好饿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 我们去稍微吃点东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:07:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:08:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这糕点是我们做好事 人家送的谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.43,0:08:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说好要和那位小姑娘一起分享的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.69,0:08:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是闹鬼的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔不会出事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能看到叔叔的屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 你留下来看家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去和住在附近的师傅打声招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你绝对不能进入这个房间哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.87,0:09:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可怕的妖怪们睡在里面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 亮堂堂的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个很可怕的妖怪睡在里面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪会睡觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都听不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会有这么多书在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.13,0:11:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和妈妈那本书是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了 师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.92,0:11:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您近来无恙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老个一两岁而已 能有什么变化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你啊 脸上褶子多起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是笑出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.31,0:12:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好酒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.23,0:12:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是师傅教我用蜂蜜酿制的酒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经没什么可教你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经成为一位出色的养蜂人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你特意登门拜访
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.97,0:12:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有事要和我商量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 我从河边捡到一个小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在和我生活在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我教她的东西能够举一反三
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个非常聪明的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.46,0:12:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在有点迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏知草
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是什么花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它叫做夏知草
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生长于日…足的…山…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然生长于日照充足的丘陵及山野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.52,0:13:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不会读 就跳过去这样可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.22,0:13:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日照充足…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丘陵?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来教你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个文字的每个笔画 都是有寓意的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:13:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的是山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.37,0:14:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山…花…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弑羊草
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个我知道 弑羊草
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个草里…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.10,0:14:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不在家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门大敞着 真是粗心大意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有坏人随随便便进去怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.18,0:14:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.39,0:14:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个小女孩 记性这么好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像苔藓吸水一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的话一句一句都装进脑子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当她解开疑问的时候 眼睛里就会散发光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎让多萨纳·约翰的血液沸腾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不用多萨纳这名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算让那些往事一直牵绊你到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使再有才能的小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.86,0:16:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有为她引路的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也无法成长起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我教你养蜂一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也去为那孩子引路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 她在 她在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到她了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 这个我们一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是别人作为感谢送给我们吃的点心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是偷别人的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢吃点心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像看书入了神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们到那边去等她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等就等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳没有察觉到鲁库和莫库的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专心地读着书
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边回忆着母亲教给她的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边出神地看着这本有关毒草的书
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔你们怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个点心吃了之后 肚子就
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个已经馊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没发现啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的肚子好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.51,0:17:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治疗用的毒…毒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏知草
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏知草
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说 要是这样舔了的话会中毒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 微小量的话还可以入药用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏知草的花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把花…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.54,0:18:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个字读什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难喝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不全喝完是不会好的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难喝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你进了那屋间是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:19:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你叫我不要进去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真知道这是一本有关毒草的书
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上过学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 是我妈妈教我认字的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.57,0:20:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这本是高级职业学校社会层的学生 16岁时学的课本
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是基本上都看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅凭着能看懂的那一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么说就让我放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这么大的孩子要是能读懂这本书
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那学舍里的教导师长们就要被赶回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 请问 这本书的名字要怎么念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它叫做 动物百态
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.94,0:20:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是介绍有关动物的种种知识的书
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想不想都读懂这些书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想 我想读懂各种各样的书
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后学习更多的知识 成为像妈妈那样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 等搬好家以后 在工作中慢慢教你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.31,0:21:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.42,0:21:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也教教你们如何分辨腐烂不可吃的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夏之山
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.15,0:21:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏之山?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.41,0:21:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟来的话 就来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.64,0:22:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总归还能吃上一口饭的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.27,0:22:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 也得你们好好干活才行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.42,0:22:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.84,0:22:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.50,0:22:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰决定把自己所学的知识都教授给艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.35,0:22:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他感觉到 接下来在夏之山的生活 也会变得越来越热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.93,0:24:02.56,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.81,0:24:04.96,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们终于搬来这个夏之小屋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.24,0:24:07.80,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米饭很可口 空气也清新
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.47,0:24:12.32,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在山的斜对面有很多美丽的春花
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.59,0:24:14.25,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我喜欢的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.91,0:24:18.98,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会见到很多你没见过的东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.30,0:24:20.70,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 很期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.52,0:24:22.71,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兽之奏者 艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.02,0:24:24.20,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白银的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.00,0:24:30.00,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,255)}白银的羽毛


